attributes.title: app leads to tragedy 💔
attributes.review: i first installed this app because i really wanted to support our country’s representative cheeto, but nevertheless, it led to a tragedy that forever changed me 😔 i was walking down the street listening to my favorite cheeto podcast and walking my pet egret when suddenly i got a notification from this app. i was soo excited to look at my phone that my precious egret managed to escape. i never managed to find her 😢 i ran home crying and saw that my sister was making the regular sautéed ice for the family supper 🥰 she quickly ran over to comfort me while i sobbed in her arms. since we weren’t in the kitchen, our pet groundhog hopped up on the stovetop and tried eating our sautéed ice, but that caused his tail to catch on fire 🔥 we didn’t notice until we saw him running around the house and by that time it was too late ,,, our house eventually burned to the ground because of this incident and the only thing that we could save was our precious family size cheeto bag ‼️ right now me and my sister are living in a dumpster behind the local burger king and surviving off of the moldy food that people throw to us 😸 none of this would have ever happened if i never downloaded this app. i am disgusted by this app and i lost trust in the big cheeto that runs it 👎🏼 i’m so sorry to all of the other people who have experienced something similar to what i had to go through 😿 i just hope someday i will be able to recover and live a normal life again 🙂,,, anyways stan loona for clear skin 💖👩🏻✨
